                        "description": "## Hybrid Search\n\nSearch research documents using a combination of BM25 keyword matching and SPECTER2 semantic embeddings.\n\n### Request Body\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n| `query` | string | ✅ | Search query (1-500 characters) |\n| `page` | integer | ❌ | Page number (default: 1) |\n| `per_page` | integer | ❌ | Results per page (1-100, default: 20) |\n| `sort` | string | ❌ | Sort order: `relevance`, `date`, `citations` |\n| `filters` | object | ❌ | Filter options (see below) |\n| `search_in` | array | ❌ | Fields to search: `title`, `abstract`, `author`, `subject_area`, `field` |\n\n### Filter Options\n\n| Field | Type | Description |\n|-------|------|-------------|\n| `year_from` | integer | Minimum publication year |\n| `year_to` | integer | Maximum publication year |\n| `field_associated` | string | Department/field filter |\n| `document_type` | string | Article, Review, Conference Paper, etc. |\n| `subject_area` | array | Subject area codes |\n\n### Response\n\nReturns matching documents with facets for filtering and pagination info."
                    },
                    "response": [
                        {
                            "name": "Success - Results Found",
                            "originalRequest": {
                                "method": "POST",
                                "header": [],
                                "body": {
                                    "mode": "raw",
                                    "raw": "{\n    \"query\": \"polymer\"\n}"
                                },
                                "url": {
                                    "raw": "{{base_url}}/search",
                                    "host": [
                                        "{{base_url}}"
                                    ],
                                    "path": [
                                        "search"
                                    ]
                                }
                            },
                            "status": "OK",
                            "code": 200,
                            "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
                            "body": "{\n    \"results\": [\n        {\n            \"_id\": \"693ea76583acace877692939\",\n            \"title\": \"Interaction potential between polymer grafted nanosheets\",\n            \"abstract\": \"We examine the polymer mediated interaction...\",\n            \"authors\": [\n                {\n                    \"author_name\": \"Chokshi, P.\",\n                    \"author_affiliation\": \"Indian Institute of Technology Delhi\"\n                }\n            ],\n            \"publication_year\": 2019,\n            \"document_type\": \"Article\",\n            \"field_associated\": \"Chemical Engineering\",\n            \"citation_count\": 6\n        }\n    ],\n    \"facets\": {\n        \"years\": [{\"value\": 2024, \"count\": 79}],\n        \"document_types\": [{\"value\": \"Article\", \"count\": 150}],\n        \"fields\": [{\"value\": \"Chemical Engineering\", \"count\": 45}]\n    },\n    \"pagination\": {\n        \"page\": 1,\n        \"per_page\": 20,\n        \"total\": 250,\n        \"total_pages\": 13\n    },\n    \"cacheHit\": false\n}"
                        }
