                        "description": "## Search with Filters\n\nSearch with year range, field, and document type filters applied.\n\n### Example Filters\n- **Year Range**: 2020-2024\n- **Field**: Computer Science\n- **Document Type**: Article\n- **Sort**: By citation count (most cited first)"
