                {
                    "name": "Search by Author (N-gram)",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n    \"query\": \"Sharma\",\n    \"search_in\": [\"author\"],\n    \"per_page\": 20\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/search",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "search"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "## Search by Author Name\n\nSearch specifically in author names using N-gram partial matching.\n\n### N-gram Matching\nThe API uses N-gram analyzers (2-4 characters) for partial matching:\n- Searching \"Sha\" will match \"Sharma\", \"Shah\", \"Shankar\"\n- Searching \"Kumar\" will match all variations\n\n### `search_in` Options\n- `author` - Author names only\n- `title` - Paper titles only\n- `abstract` - Abstracts only\n- `subject_area` - Subject areas\n- `field` - Associated fields"
                    },
                    "response": []
                },
                {
                    "name": "Search by Subject Area",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n    \"query\": \"Engineering\",\n    \"search_in\": [\"subject_area\", \"field\"],\n    \"per_page\": 20\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/search",
                            "host": [
                                "{{base_url}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "search"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "## Search by Subject Area or Field\n\nSearch specifically in subject areas and associated fields.\n\n### Example\nSearching \"Eng\" will match:\n- \"Chemical Engineering\"\n- \"Mechanical Engineering\"\n- \"Environmental Engineering\"\n\n### Combined Field Search\nYou can search in multiple fields by providing an array:\n```json\n\"search_in\": [\"subject_area\", \"field\"]\n```"
                    },
                    "response": []
                },
